```

## ğŸ¨ **Perubahan Visual dalam Icon Mode**

### **1. Sidebar Width**
```scss
[data-sidebar="icon"] {
    .pe-app-sidebar {
        width: var(--pe-app-sidebar-sm-width); // 80px
    }
}
```

### **2. Hide Text & Arrows**
```scss
[data-sidebar="icon"] {
    .pe-menu-title {
        display: none; // Sembunyikan judul menu
    }
    
    .pe-nav-content, .pe-nav-arrow {
        display: none; // Sembunyikan teks & panah
    }
}
```

### **3. Center Icons**
```scss
[data-sidebar="icon"] {
    .pe-nav-icon {
        margin: 0 auto; // Icon di tengah
    }
}
```

### **4. Hover Dropdown Menu**
```scss
[data-sidebar="icon"] {
    .pe-slide-menu {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.9375rem;
        left: var(--pe-app-sidebar-sm-width); // 80px dari kiri
        width: 11.7rem; // 187px lebar dropdown
        background: var(--pe-app-sidebar-bg);
        border-radius: var(--pe-border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--pe-box-shadow-sm);
        
        // Awalnya tersembunyi
        opacity: 0;
        visibility: hidden;
    }
    
    .pe-slide:hover .pe-slide-menu {
        opacity: 1;
        visibility: visible; // Tampil saat hover
    }
}
```

## ğŸ”„ **State Management**

### **HTML Attribute Control**
```html
<!-- Mode Normal -->
<html data-sidebar="default">

<!-- Mode Icon -->
<html data-sidebar="icon">
```

### **Local Storage**
```javascript
// Menyimpan preferensi user
localStorage.setItem('data-sidebar', 'icon');

// Memuat preferensi saat page load
const savedSidebar = localStorage.getItem('data-sidebar') || 'default';
htmlElement.setAttribute('data-sidebar', savedSidebar);
```

## ğŸ“± **Responsive Behavior**

### **Desktop (â‰¥992px)**
```scss
@include media-breakpoint-up(lg) {
    [data-sidebar="icon"] {
        .app-header {
            left: var(--pe-app-sidebar-sm-width); // Header bergeser
        }
        
        .app-wrapper, .footer {
            margin-inline-start: var(--pe-app-sidebar-sm-width); // Content bergeser
        }
    }
}
```

### **Mobile (<992px)**
```javascript
if (window.innerWidth < 992) {
    // Di mobile, toggle show/hide sidebar overlay
    const sidebar = document.getElementById("sidebar");
    sidebar.classList.add("show");
} else {
    // Di desktop, toggle icon mode
    htmlElement.setAttribute("data-sidebar", "icon");
}
```

## ğŸ›  **Implementasi untuk Backend Developer**

### **1. Blade Template Integration**
```php
<!-- Di layout utama -->
<html data-sidebar="{{ session('sidebar_mode', 'default') }}">

<!-- Controller untuk menyimpan preferensi -->
public function setSidebarMode(Request $request)
{
    session(['sidebar_mode' => $request->mode]);
    return response()->json(['status' => 'success']);
}
```

### **2. Route untuk AJAX**
```php
// routes/web.php
Route::post('/set-sidebar-mode', [LayoutController::class, 'setSidebarMode']);
```

### **3. JavaScript AJAX Call**
```javascript
// Simpan ke server saat toggle
toggleButton?.addEventListener("click", () => {
    const newMode = currentToggled === "icon" ? "default" : "icon";
    
    // Update UI
    htmlElement.setAttribute("data-sidebar", newMode);
    
    // Simpan ke server
    fetch('/set-sidebar-mode', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: {
            'Content-Type': 'application/json',
            'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').content
        },
        body: JSON.stringify({ mode: newMode })
    });
});
```

## âš¡ **Performance Considerations**

### **1. CSS Transitions**
```scss
.pe-app-sidebar {
    transition: width 0.3s ease; // Smooth animation
}

.pe-slide-menu {
    transition: opacity 0.2s ease, visibility 0.2s ease;
}
```

### **2. Hardware Acceleration**
```scss
.pe-slide-menu {
    transform: translateZ(0); // GPU acceleration
    will-change: opacity, visibility;
}
```

## ğŸ¯ **Key Points untuk Backend Developer**

### **âœ… Yang Perlu Dipahami:**

1. **State Control**: Sistem menggunakan `data-sidebar` attribute pada `<html>`
2. **CSS Cascade**: Semua styling dikontrol oleh `[data-sidebar="icon"]` selector
3. **Responsive**: Behavior berbeda untuk desktop vs mobile
4. **Session Storage**: Preferensi user bisa disimpan di session/database
5. **AJAX Integration**: Bisa diintegrasikan dengan backend untuk menyimpan preferensi

### **ğŸ”§ Yang Bisa Dikustomisasi:**

1. **Ukuran sidebar**: Ubah `$app-sidebar-sm-width` di `_custom-variables.scss`
2. **Animation speed**: Ubah `transition` duration di CSS
3. **Dropdown positioning**: Ubah `left` dan `top` values
4. **Colors & themes**: Sesuaikan dengan brand colors

### **âš ï¸ Yang Harus Diperhatikan:**

1. **Z-index conflicts**: Pastikan dropdown menu tidak tertutup elemen lain
2. **Mobile compatibility**: Test di berbagai ukuran layar
3. **Accessibility**: Pastikan keyboard navigation tetap berfungsi
4. **Performance**: Hindari terlalu banyak DOM manipulation

Sistem ini sudah **production-ready** dan mengikuti **best practices** untuk responsive design dan user experience!
        